   Recreation Areas
   The State Vehicular Recreation Areas or SVRAs, are OHV parks that are
   owned and operated by the OHMVR Division of California State Parks.
   Find out more on the six different State Vehicle Recreation Areas.
   [spacer.gif] [wedge.gif] Recreation Areas
   [tread.gif]

   Conservation Efforts
   In an age where outdoor recreation is the sport of choice, it is our
   responsibility to exercise responsible outdoor practices. Find out
   about CIWMB and how new regulations will result in changes in OHV
   programs.
   [spacer.gif] [wedge.gif] Conservation Efforts
   [offroad-Kids.jpg]

   Off-Road PALs
   Off-Road Pals has helped reach out to Californias diverse urban youth
   and has provided more than 1,500 students positive and life-changing
   experiences.
   [spacer.gif] [wedge.gif] Off-Road PALs



